void eol_opengl_get_gl_coordinate ( GLint  x,
GLint  y,
GLdouble  z,
const GLdouble *  model,
const GLdouble *  proj,
const GLint *  view,
GLdouble *  glx,
GLdouble *  gly,
GLdouble *  glz 
)

calculated the 3D position for the given 2D position at the depth provided

Parameters:
x the 2D space x position
y the 2D space y position
z the depth into 3D space to calculate the projection
model the current gl model
proj the current gl projection
view the current gl view
glx the output projected x position in 3D
gly the output projected x position in 3D
glz the output projected z position in 3D
